   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="tl057a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <name type="place">Knoxville</name>
                     <date when="1804-04-04">4 April 1804</date>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <salute>Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>Permit me to trouble you with An address <add place="supralinear">which</add> I beg you to forward <add place="supralinear">directed</add> to the <del type="overstrike">inhabit</del>
		  people said to be <add place="supralinear">settled and</add> intruding upon the
		  Indian lands. I am officially informed by the Agent of the War department that
		  there is a considerable number of <del type="overstrike">those</del> persons
		  settled on those lands, and I also understand that the regular troops
		  <add place="supralinear">are shortly</add>
               <del type="overstrike">is
		  about</del> to be employed for their removal I <add place="supralinear">therefore</add> deem it expedient to <del type="overstrike">
                  <choice>
                     <orig>fore warn</orig>
                     <reg>forewarn</reg>
                  </choice> them</del> give them
		  information of the dangers they may <del type="overstrike">be</del> expose<del type="overstrike">d</del> themselves to, should they be found trespassing as
		  has been to me represented</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>I have the honor  
				<choice>
                     <abbr>C</abbr>
                     <expan>et cetera</expan>
                  </choice>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>J.</abbr>
                        <expan>John</expan>
                     </choice> Sevier</name>
                  <address>
                     <addrLine>
                        <name type="person">
                           <choice>
                              <abbr>Colo.</abbr>
                              <expan>Colonel</expan>
                           </choice> Hugh
						Montgomery</name>
                     </addrLine>
                     <addrLine>
                        <name type="place">Anderson County</name>
                     </addrLine>
                  </address>
               </signed>
            </closer>
         </div>
